      <div class="msgContentFrame">Agreed. Feint at rank 20 is the best ability I've seen for Disciplines of War hands down. My PUG/GLAD friends really wish they had it lol. <br /> <br />Small stamina cost, 250 TP to use, (it's practically stamina management) and will deal 200+ unavoidable damage to the target. Can only be activated after missing or being evaded. It's your ticket to an assured kill. <br /><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2639653" title="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2639653" rel="external nofollow">http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2639653</a></div></div>
