      <div class="msgContentFrame">If you have another class leveled to high teens at least, you should have no issues with missing for quite a while on your lancer. Most people with issues started as lancer and powered through, meaning they had less stat points. Its still doable that way, but every DoW class has issues missing if they have no gear or stat advantages.  <br /> <br />My advice is go 40 vit, then 40 dex, then 40 str. After that, go str to cap ( 2*level+32) with extra in vit. Buy 4 brass rings. They are cheap.  <br /> <br />Take conjurer to 8 before leveling lancer past 10. Use shock spikes on any non-trivial mob. Its better than any healing ability. Second wind is probably the best healing ability you can use. If you need multiple heals, you shouldnt be fighting it. Cure takes too long for too little on tough mobs. I ended up dropping it and not using any healing until I got to 20, now I use bloodbath. Speed surge is good enough most of the time. I rarely use bloodbath.  <br /> <br /></div>
